name: Manhattan
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1
hint: Best served neat, on the rocks masks the powerful fragrance.

ingredients:
  - (2 oz)     Rye Whisky
  - (1 oz)     Sweet Vermouth
  - (1 dash)   Angostura Bitters
  - (1 twist)  Lemon Rind

steps:
  - Pour rye and vermouth into a rocks glass
  - Add a dash of bitters
  - Drop in lemon twist garnish
